== Methods · ways of working

- *Solo work* --- end-to-end ownership: research code, infrastructure, writing, deploy.
- *Team work* --- international collaborations (research papers), JICA scholar, YuLab seminars.
- *Mentorship* --- TA &amp; RA at Hosei IIST; ESATIC mentor (15+ undergraduates); volunteer lecturer at 2 Japanese high schools.
- *Cross-cultural* --- comfortable across Japan, the Gulf, and West Africa, in French / English / Japanese.
- *Writing under deadline pressure* --- 11 of 12 first-author submissions accepted across journals and conferences.
- *Reproducible research* --- version control, evaluation harnesses, ablations, multi-seed validation.

